<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Certificat Halal — Poulets BF</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bf-green: #2E7D32;
      --bf-green-dark: #14532D;
      --bf-green-light: #E8F5E9;
      --bf-amber: #FF8F00;
      --bf-red: #CE1126;
      --bf-yellow: #FCD116;
      --ink: #0F172A;
      --ink-soft: #475569;
      --ink-muted: #94A3B8;
      --paper: #FFFFFF;
      --border-fine: #D1D5DB;
    }

    @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--paper);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 210mm; min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 12mm 15mm;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Watermark sécurité */
    .page::before {
      content: 'HALAL';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-25deg);
      font-size: 160pt;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(46, 125, 50, 0.04);
      letter-spacing: 8pt;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      border-bottom: 3pt solid var(--bf-green);
      padding-bottom: 6mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4mm;
    }
    .brand-logo {
      width: 18mm; height: 18mm;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bf-green) 0%, var(--bf-amber) 100%);
      color: #FFFFFF;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 16pt;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .brand-text strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 16pt;
      color: var(--bf-green);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .brand-text span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .flag-strip {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 20mm;
      border: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
    }
    .flag-strip div { height: 8mm; }
    .flag-red { background: var(--bf-red); }
    .flag-green-strip { background: var(--bf-green); }
    .flag-star {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 6mm;
      background: #FFFFFF;
      color: var(--bf-yellow);
      font-size: 10pt;
    }

    .title-banner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bf-green-dark), var(--bf-green));
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 8mm;
      border-radius: 3pt;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .title-banner h1 {
      font-size: 26pt;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1pt;
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }
    .title-banner p {
      font-size: 11pt;
      opacity: 0.95;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .recipient {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 10mm;
    }
    .recipient-label {
      font-size: 9pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1pt;
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }
    .recipient-name {
      font-size: 22pt;
      color: var(--bf-green-dark);
      font-weight: 700;
      border-bottom: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      padding-bottom: 3mm;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-inline: 20mm;
    }

    .certify-text {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--ink-soft);
      text-align: justify;
      padding: 0 8mm;
      margin-bottom: 8mm;
    }
    .certify-text strong { color: var(--bf-green-dark); }

    .details {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3mm 8mm;
      background: var(--bf-green-light);
      border-left: 4pt solid var(--bf-green);
      padding: 6mm 8mm;
      margin-bottom: 10mm;
    }
    .details dt {
      font-size: 8pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
    }
    .details dd {
      font-size: 11pt;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 2mm;
    }

    .signature-zone {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
      gap: 8mm;
      align-items: end;
      margin-bottom: 6mm;
    }
    .sig-block {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 12mm;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--ink);
    }
    .sig-block strong { display: block; font-size: 10pt; }
    .sig-block span { display: block; font-size: 9pt; color: var(--ink-soft); }

    .qr-block {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2mm;
      border: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      background: #FFFFFF;
    }
    .qr-block img {
      width: 25mm; height: 25mm;
      display: block;
    }
    .qr-block span {
      display: block;
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      margin-top: 1mm;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }

    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 8mm; left: 15mm; right: 15mm;
      font-size: 7pt;
      color: var(--ink-muted);
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1pt solid var(--border-fine);
      padding-top: 3mm;
    }
    .footer strong { color: var(--ink-soft); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-logo">{{#if logoLetter}}{{logoLetter}}{{else}}P{{/if}}</div>
        <div class="brand-text">
          <strong>Poulets BF</strong>
          <span>FASO DIGITALISATION · Burkina Faso</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flag-strip" title="Drapeau Burkina Faso">
        <div class="flag-red"></div>
        <div class="flag-star">★</div>
        <div class="flag-green-strip"></div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="title-banner">
      <h1>Certificat Halal</h1>
      <p>Attestation de conformité religieuse · Lot avicole</p>
    </section>

    <section class="recipient">
      <div class="recipient-label">Délivré à</div>
      <div class="recipient-name">{{eleveurName}}</div>
    </section>

    <p class="certify-text">
      Nous attestons que le lot <strong>{{lotId}}</strong> de <strong>{{quantity}} sujets</strong>
      de race <strong>{{race}}</strong>, élevé par <strong>{{eleveurName}}</strong> à
      <strong>{{region}}</strong>, a été abattu en stricte conformité avec les pratiques
      halal, sous la supervision du sacrificateur agréé et après contrôle vétérinaire.
      La traçabilité complète est accessible via le QR code ci-dessous.
    </p>

    <dl class="details">
      <div>
        <dt>Numéro de lot</dt>
        <dd>{{lotId}}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Quantité certifiée</dt>
        <dd>{{quantity}} sujets</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Abattoir agréé</dt>
        <dd>{{abattoir}}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Sacrificateur</dt>
        <dd>{{sacrificateur}}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Vétérinaire</dt>
        <dd>{{veterinaire}}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Date d'abattage</dt>
        <dd>{{dateAbattage}}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Validité</dt>
        <dd>{{validite}}</dd>
      </div>
      <div>
        <dt>Certificat N°</dt>
        <dd>{{certifId}}</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>

    <section class="signature-zone">
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Éleveur responsable</strong>
        <span>{{eleveurName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="qr-block">
        <img src="{{qrCodeDataUri}}" alt="QR vérification">
        <span>{{certifId}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="sig-block">
        <strong>Autorité de certification</strong>
        <span>Poulets BF · FASO DIGITALISATION</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
      Document officiel — <strong>{{issuedAt}}</strong> —
      Vérification en ligne : {{verificationUrl}}<br>
      © FASO DIGITALISATION — Conforme aux lois du Burkina Faso
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
